WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.713
If a trainee forgets their password, the trainer resets it.

00:00:03.713 --> 00:00:07.174
And the trainer recovers theirs with the recovery code:

00:00:07.174 --> 00:00:12.460
under “Forgot my password”, they enter the username and the code, and set a new one.
